01:44.200 --> 01:44.840
Kasut dan jaket kulit.

01:44.840 --> 01:45.979
Semuanya dah berjalan lancar.

01:45.979 --> 01:46.780
Jadi saya minta kilang

01:46.780 --> 01:48.020
berurusan secara terus.

01:48.020 --> 01:49.400
Kami berdua dah jumpa satu kedai

01:49.400 --> 01:50.259
di Jalan Yabao.

01:50.460 --> 01:51.120
Kami fikir nak

01:51.120 --> 01:52.440
